column4: NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "6E7F34864432601DC74C8D80503B2B43", "This tunnel hasn\'t been opened yet. Don\'t get in our way.")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "1C634468457E2F56B6490091B082DC23", "I\'m sorry. Do you know when it will be?")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "7B2267354A8D029B341ABAB25664B2B9", "I don\'t know, it will take a while.")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "09F269E948B2F7E75F71CA87A2BFCAFF", "Are you trying to steal our fun? Maybe you can carry dirt.")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "B31C6CCC4BB6F8CA3B3238AE8DD108A5", "I dug up that dirt. You can carry it out and dump it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "588BA34E43E3C332EB44FCA35AA5E306", "It\'s a hard job, so I\'ll pay you five hund bits for each round trip.")
NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "3D002555475530463032DC9D175FFC49", "This will make digging go faster. I can make money, and it\'s good training.")

NSLOCTEXT("[10D22215493A910DD4679EBD0B883B13]", "5534067F45883558B82AEF804D9527BC", "Use [E] to set a dirt box in front of dirt. Dump dirt outside tunnel. Once you finish a round, please tell Drimogemon.")
